Date: Tue, 20 Dec 2005 14:38:04 +0100
Subject: [RsR] Package name vote --> 'robustbase'
In-Reply-To: <17313.40798.623273.319760@stat.math.ethz.ch>
References: <5.1.0.14.2.20051210193001.023cfaf0@pop.intranet.chuv>
	<17312.13921.354305.320499@stat.math.ethz.ch>
